---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Cleaner Standards | CamCleans";
const description =
  "CamCleans maintains clear service standards for cleaners operating through the network across the United Kingdom.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/cleaner-standards">

<section class="section">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Trust</span>
<h2>Cleaner Standards</h2>
<p>
CamCleans maintains clear service standards to ensure cleaning jobs are completed reliably and professionally. These standards help create consistency for customers and cleaners across the United Kingdom.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>Professional conduct</h3>
<p>
Cleaners are expected to communicate clearly, arrive on time and complete work respectfully within the customer’s property.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Service reliability</h3>
<p>
Accepted jobs must be completed as agreed. If circumstances change the customer must be informed as early as possible.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Attention to detail</h3>
<p>
Cleaning work should meet the checklist requirements for the service type requested by the customer.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Property care</h3>
<p>
Cleaners must take care when working inside homes or rental properties and respect furniture, surfaces and belongings.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Clear expectations</h3>
<p>
Service descriptions and checklists help both cleaners and customers understand what is included in each job.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Quality monitoring</h3>
<p>
Job outcomes are monitored to help maintain consistent standards across the network.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>


<section class="section section-tight">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Services</span>
<h2>Cleaning services covered</h2>
<p>
CamCleans enquiries commonly include several types of domestic and property cleaning services.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>End of tenancy cleaning</h3>
<p>
Inspection ready cleaning designed for tenants and landlords preparing a property for handover.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Deep cleaning</h3>
<p>
Thorough cleaning for properties that require a more detailed service than routine domestic cleaning.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>After builders cleaning</h3>
<p>
Cleaning following renovation or construction work to remove dust and residue.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>


<section class="section">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Join</span>
<h2>Work through the CamCleans network</h2>
<p>
Independent cleaners and small cleaning teams can apply to receive work through CamCleans.
</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/join-cleaners">
Join the cleaner network
</a>
</div>

</div>
</section>

</Layout>